data.description: An excellent opportunity to own your home or make the right investment move. This property is located in a calm neighborhood on 14 mile Road and Ryan Road, which is a prime location on the border line of Sterling Heights and Warren. With some cosmetic updates, this property can turn into a gem. The property features include: a semi open concept with the kitchen being open to the dining area and the living room with an electric fire place, a spacious family room facing the front of the house, three nice sized bedrooms, a good size full bathroom as well as another half bath. Don't miss the opportunity to own this ideal properly. Buyer's agent is to verify all information. For questions or details, reach out directly to Aziz Mariya.
